{"name":"King Frederick IV","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Fenwick, King","alignment":"Chaotic Neutral","hitDice":"16","armorName":"plate","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":-9,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"18","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"12","wisPoints":"20","chaPoints":"16","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Diplomatic Visbility","desc":"[MON] can cast Detect Thoughts at will without concentration. When [MON] has Detect Thoughts active, he learns everything on the player's character sheet."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON]'s spellcasting ability is Wisdom (spell save DC [WIS SAVE], [WIS ATK] to hit).\n\n> 1st level (2 slots): _Command, Bane_\n> 2nd level (4 slots): _Zone of Truth, Detect Thoughts, Suggestion, Spiritual Weapon_\n> 3rd level (1 slots): _Dispel Magic, Motivational Speech_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two weapon attacks."},{"name":"Swords of Revealing Light","desc":"[MON] attacks a creature with one of his floating, spectral swords. [STR ATK] to hit, range 20/60 ft. _Hit:_ [STR 1D12] radiant damage. Creatures hit by the swords start glowing, lose all disguises, and reverts to their true form."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Whispers of Treachery","desc":"[MON] sows seeds of doubt and betrayal in [1d4] creatures in can see. They must make a **DC [WIS SAVE]** Wisdom Save or become charmed for 1 minute, or until they take damage from [MON]."},{"name":"Reconissance","desc":"[MON] chooses [1d4] creatures it's reading the thoughts of, and **concentrates** on those thoughts to learn about their next moves. [MON] gains advantage on saves against those creatures, and those creatures have disadvantage on attacks against [MON]."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"deception","stat":"cha","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"investigation","stat":"int"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Frederick","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":2,"damage":[]}